Security Features
- KMS-backed encryption for documents.
- Secrets stored in AWS Secrets Manager.
- IAM-based access control.
- Unique employee IDs.
- Temporary passwords generated automatically.
API Endpoints
POST /api/onboard
GET /api/employees
GET /api/employee/<emp_id>/secret
GET /api/employee/<emp_id>/document/<doc_name>
